WEBVTT

00:07:59.458 --> 00:08:00.708
and love.

00:08:01.958 --> 00:08:06.101
Because, creative expression in any form

00:08:06.125 --> 00:08:08.309
is generative.

00:08:08.333 --> 00:08:12.976
It helps make beauty and meaning and value

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:16.083
where there might have been
absolutely nothing before.

00:08:17.542 --> 00:08:21.434
If we can infuse
that creativity into care,

00:08:21.458 --> 00:08:26.309
caregivers can invite a partner
into meaning-making,

00:08:26.333 --> 00:08:29.559
and in that moment, care,

00:08:29.583 --> 00:08:33.476
which is so often associated with loss,